Author: NickelCoin
Title: [ANN] *NICKELCOIN* Deploying Blockchain Technology to Customer's Loyalty Rewards
Body: The Idea behind Nickelcoin is to replace Physical cards with digital cards... customers earn reward points for their buying activities in any of the merchant stores connected to Nickelcoin... Merchants can also give out discount coupons or send digital gift cards (with unique QR) to any of their desired customers... You can redeem this points at the merchant store but if you receive reward points in any store you don't visit often, You can trade these points with other retailers in the Nickelcoin exchange platform... Please read our Whitepaper to get all the details  Thanks

Title: [ANN] *NICKELCOIN* Deploying Blockchain Technology to Customer's Loyalty Rewards
Body: Hello, Regulators in countries across the globe are taking an increasing interest in ICOs. This creates uncertainty for both Offerers and for those who want to invest. So, Nickelcoin ICO is a genuine and Long-term project and we fully comply with international Anti-Money Laundering legislation. Nickelcoin Ico sales is not available for Ico restricted countries and we will cooperate with law enforcement agencies if requested by them, OR if we identify activity that looks to be criminal in nature (Which is why we implemented the "Know Your Customer" (KYC) in our ICO.  Most importantly: Cryptocurrency exchanges are beginning to exclude cryptocurrencies that did not properly implement KYC processes. Thus, not running such checks poses a long-term risk to our project.  Hope You Understand our Reasons..  Thanks

Author: NickelCoin
Title: [ANN] *NICKELCOIN* Deploying Blockchain Technology to Customer's Loyalty Rewards
Body: WEBSITE    FACEBOOK    TWITTER    TELEGRAM   LINKEDIN    GITHUB     BOUNTY  NICKELCOIN    DEPLOYING BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY TO CUSTOMER'S LOYALTY REWARDS    Many retailers and consumers pill-up their gift cards, reward points, discount coupons without being used.  That is why we came up with NICKELCOIN  Nickelcoin transforms traditional discount coupons, loyalty points and shopping vouchers into liquid, tradable digital tokens.  Nickelcoin is a global wallet for customers Loyalty Rewards. With Nickelcoin, You can manage all your reward points in one place.   Name: Nickelcoin  Symbol: NKL  Total Coin Supply: 40,000,000  Decimal: 8  ERC20 Token  Smart Contract Address: 0xBD60d6dB0B4fBfa01e4EE1C69A8d1510638f0DeB   What Does Nickelcoin Offer??   1. Nickelcoin offers a market platform based solution which will include an internal blockchain network employing the new cryptocurrency NICKELCOIN.  2. Nickelcoin Global Customer Loyalty Services offers a modern user-friendly loyalty Apps which replaces the standard physical loyalty card.  3. We offer a highly secure platform for storing, transferring and trading of digital assets including Nickelcoin.  4. A global Market Place offering products, rewards and gifts items for our loyal customers.   So, with Nickelcoin blockchain technology, you will never loss reward points anymore.  You can also redeem your discount coupons or points from our merchant store, but if you receive points from stores you don?t visit often, With Nickelcoin internal exchange, you can trade your reward points and discount tokens with other retailers and receive tokens which increase in value.  What About Retailers and Businesses?  With Nickelcoin, Retailers don?t have to be blockchain experts to use our Loyalty services; they can simply connect to the Nickelcoin loyalty system by installing the ready-made GIFTED extension or by integrating it with their own loyalty system. This idea will reward customers with Nickelcoin for their buying activities or purchases as well as other actions.  Not just all, with Nickelcoin A-drop functionality, merchants can send their tokens directly to customers based on their Location, Demography and Spending Habits, and that?s great for business as this helps in gaining market insight.    Sounds great Right?  Cool, that's why we created it.  Don't miss this Global Marketing innovation.  Join Nickelcoin ICO  FEATURES  Payment Gateway Providing a smooth incorporation Payment Gateways  UniverUser-Friendlyewards Modern User-Friendly Loyalty Platform and Apps which replaces the standard physical Loyalty Card.  Market Place Retail tokens can be used to buy products, get discounts or claim rewards from merchants.
